Package commands

Class AbstractCommand

java.lang.Object
commands.AbstractCommand
Direct Known Subclasses:
AddCommand, AddIfMaxCommand, ClearCommand, ExecuteScriptCommand, ExitCommand, FilterStartsWFullNameCommand, HeadCommand, HelpCommand, InfoCommand, MinByCreationDateCommand, PrintUniqPostalAddCommand, RemoveByIdCommand, RemoveLowerCommand, RollBackCommand, SaveCommand, ShowCommand, UpdateCommand
public abstract class AbstractCommand extends Object
The AbstractCommand class represents a template for implementing command objects in the command pattern. It encapsulates common attributes and behaviors of commands such as name and description.
